and force thousands more out of work temporarily.

12
00:00:37,599 --> 00:00:40,960
With no idea if their job will still be there when they return.

13
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:45,599
For those daily workers without savings to pay the rent and feed their families,

14
00:00:45,599 --> 00:00:47,599
it's been especially stressful.

15
00:00:48,159 --> 00:00:51,519
Each job loss is a potential personal tragedy.

16
