In this programme, we'll be assessing the post-COVID job landscape

17
00:00:55,359 --> 00:01:00,799
and asking whether a radical new approach is needed to prevent global mass unemployment.

18
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:06,480
We'll be asking whether one of the world's smallest and richest countries, Denmark,

19
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,840
might hold the answer.

20
